overview: On January 7th GCW presents Save Me live on FITE+ straight from Thalia Hall in Chicago, IL. The first matches from the lineup are already announced and you can check them below:  THRUSSY (Effy, Allie, Sheik) vs Mason'S Mercenaries (Mason, Slade, Parrow)  Joey Janela vs Tony Deppen  Cole Radrick vs Arez  Macizos vs Bang Bros  Christian Blake vs Liam Slater  Homicide vs JWM
title: GCW Save Me
